d to solve this problem. As an example, we provide numerical results showing\nthe performance gap of the well-known weight adjustment method and show that\nthere is considerable room for improvement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2012 22:12:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-27"}
