 defined as those clustering less\nthan the Poisson process in the sense of void probabilities and moment\nmeasures, negative association or dcx-ordering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2012 22:16:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 May 2014 11:07:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-23"}
