an\necclesiastical network in Merovingian Gaul. An R code, called Rambo,\nimplementing the inference algorithm is available from the authors upon\nrequest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Dec 2012 15:48:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 12:47:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 May 2014 06:38:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-06"}
